Package eu.eexcess.insa.peas

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CacheReader
    This class is used to read caches.
    CachingTask
    This class is used to put the co-occurrence graph and the maximal cliques in cache.
    Clique
    A clique is represented as a weighted graph.
    CoOccurrenceGraph
    A co-occurrence graph is a weighted graph.
    QueryEngine
    Three formats of queries are handled in this component (see QueryFormats): QF1, QF2 and QF3.
    QueryLogFlushOutTask
    This class is used to flush out the query log.
    QueryLogThread
    This class is used to add a query in the log without interrupting the processing of the query.
    Scheduler
    This class represents the scheduler in charge of managing the query log and the caches.
